@startuml
!theme plain

title Dressrosa - System Context

actor Employee
actor Manager
actor HR
actor Admin

rectangle "Dressrosa Web App" {
  component "Web UI\n(Jinja2 + HTMX)" as UI
  component "FastAPI Backend" as API
  database "SQLite DB" as DB
}

Employee --> UI : Request leave\nClock in/out\nView status
Manager --> UI : Review team requests
HR --> UI : Override approvals\nMonitor leaves
Admin --> UI : Manage users/policies

UI --> API : HTTP requests
API --> DB : Read/Write

@enduml
